The '''Council Authority''' was the security force responsible for protecting and maintaining order within the [[Indu Council]] through the use of [[Authority Officer]]s.

One Authority Officer, [[Kaleb Darme]], was responsible for the assassination of chief [[Councillor/Legends|councilor]] [[Shek Barayel]] and the murder of his [[Aide/Legends|aide]], [[Tev Aden]].

